subject: America's Cup
Sailboats and Sailing
lead_paragraph: Team New Zealand’s lead, once a seemingly impregnable 8-1, has been whittled to 8-5, and this regatta, originally scheduled to end no later than Sunday, is now extending into uncharted waters.
